results.title: Wedding Personalized Hand stamped Stainless Steel THE KEEPSAKE Belly button ring hearts for names, dates, words, quote
results.description:
This can be your personalized belly ring with the names of the people in your life that you couldn't be without, wedding dates and names, or anything really.  I named it The Keepsake.

The KEEPSAKE heart charm: These 22 gauge, stainless steel hearts measure 15 mm wide by 14 mm tall. It is the perfect size for a belly ring!

These Belly Button Rings are completely personalized to your taste. You pick the color and you pick what you want stamped on the sterling silver hearts. I've stamped my family's names on the heart. You could choose names, dates, words. Small phrases. or a combination of all of those.  Depending on what you want I can do small hearts or periods to separate words.  I love making unique pieces to suit you and only you! Message me with ideas you have i will work to make them work anyway I can.

IDEAS:
Kids names
Husband and kids
Kids names with date of birth
Wedding dates 
New last name with date of wedding
Words that mean the most to you
Short phrases 
Anything you want!!


Belly Ring:
316L 14 Gauge 7/16" Gem Banana Belly Rings comes in 14 different colors. The last picture shows the color options, labeled.  If your having a hard time deciding on the color you want and would like an individual pic of the color please message me. Some belly rings are double gem some have silver balls on top, depending on my stock at the time. If you specify double gem or single gem I will try to accommodate your wishes, though this is not always possible.

*********************************************************
What I need from you: Please leave in the 'message to seller' section at checkout!

1. What you want stamped on The Keepsake heart
**********************************************************

Combined Shipping does not make the price go up. So order as many as you like and pay one low price.
INTERNATIONAL ORDERs please refer to my policy section of my store for details on shipping
http://www.etsy.com/shop/ForeverStamped/policy?ref=shopinfo_policies_leftnav

Check my store often for more unique pieces
www.ForeverStamped.etsy.com

www.Natureshealingkiss.etsy.com (organic body care items and candles)
www.Itsallgoodwood.etsy.com(all woodburned wood items)
www.Itsallchalkedup.etsy.com(all your chalkboarding needs!)
www.bellybuttonsRcute.etsy.com(all belly buttons)

*****
KEEP IN MIND when you purchase from me that I alone am stamping these products. Not a machine but a person. So human error is possible. These errors are what make handstamping unique and one of a kind. Your piece is custom made and will never be duplicated. That is the main draw amoung handstamped buyers. I have a very critical eye when I send out my products but if you are unhappy with your handstamped piece you may return it for a refund or a remake. *****

FIND ME ON FACEBOOK: www.facebook.com/4everStamped
For coupon codes, new product pictures and inspiring, uplifting words!
